#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Duggativinipātabhayasutta → vinipātasuttaṃ (bj) | duggati 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Duggativinipātabhayasutta "
msgstr "15. Fear of the Bad Place, the Underworld "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn55.15:1.1"
msgid "“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sabbaduggativinipātabhayaṃ samatikkanto hoti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a noble disciple who has four things has gone beyond all fear of being reborn in a bad place, the underworld. "

msgctxt "sn55.15:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.15:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.15:1.4"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.15:1.5"
msgid "Dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.15:1.6"
msgid "saṃghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.15:1.7"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.15:1.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sabbaduggativinipātabhayaṃ samatikkanto hotī”ti. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has these four things has gone beyond all fear of being reborn in a bad place, the underworld.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.15:1.9"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

